api

Class Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.Result
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TaskResult, ValueResult

    public abstract class Result
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Result is for containing result of a task execution, including the result Id, task start time and end time. Each result is associated with its corresponding task, both of them have the same ID.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
